name: Highlights | Guyana Amazon Warriors vs Rangpur Riders | GSL 2025
description:
Highlights between the Guyana Amazon Warriors and the Rangpur Riders in the GSL 2025 at Providence Stadium in Guyana. 

The Global Super League (GSL) T20 2025 returns for its second year in Guyana, featuring five teams from around the globe. This year's teams are Caribbean Premier League side Guyana Amazon Warriors, Dubai Capitals winners of the International League T20, GSL defending champions Rangpur Riders from the Bangladesh Premier League, Central Districts from the Super Smash in New Zealand, and Big Bash League Champions Hobart Hurricanes XI from Australia. Eleven matches, including the final, will be played across as many days starting July 10, with each team playing the other once before the top two make the final on July 19.
